<plot>In depth look into the making of the sequel to Die Hard (1988), Die Hard 2 (1990). Most of this television-aired making of features interviews with director Renny Harlin and star Bruce Willis. Several sequences are analyzed and deconstructed, showing the use of various models and taking us to the various locations in which the film was made. This is a fairly promotional piece, and was only put together to promote the film at its time of release.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?146376</url></doc>
